Typically cost share projects at 80% government and 20% industry.
Compressed Natural Gas (CNG): Continue development of lower cost tank material, and cost-effective tank manufacturing techniques, for storage of compressed natural gas for type 4 tanks.
These tanks are made with plastic liners with full-wrapped continuous fiberglass and/or carbon fibers in a resin matrix.
Begin work on advanced CNG storage concepts.
